beer.beer_description:
Brewed with coconut three ways, this Hazy IPA will change your watch to tiki time and transport you straight to the shores of Maui.

A powerful coconut punch is quickly soothes by waves of tropical hops. It’s a decadent drop that will place you front and center at the luau while your taste buds dance the hula.

Hops: Sabro, Wakatu, Cashmere, Motueka
